DOC.detailed_description: Women randomly divide 3 group ; first group undergo IUI time HCG administration , second group undergo IUI 12 hour HCG administration third group undergo IUI 34-36 hour HCG administration .
DOC.criteria: Mild male factor infertility unexplained infertility . Advanced male factor infertility . Polycystic ovary syndrome ( PCOS ) define Rotterdam criterion . Endometriosis . Tubal disease . Uterine abnormalities myoma . Previous uterine surgery . Metabolic hormonal abnormality .
